        <num>9-3-7</num>
        <content>
          <p>The statute of limitations for a mutual account begins to run on the date of the last item thereof. A mutual account must include an indebtedness on both sides. Mere entries of credits of partial payments shall not be sufficient.</p>
          <p>(Civil Code 1895, ยง 3769; Civil Code 1910, ยง 4363; Code 1933, ยง 3-707.)</p>
